Movie Notes 
~~~~~~~~~~~
Long before the first migration, there raged a Great Battle Between the Birds and the Beasts. 
This was fought to establish the balance of nature and the territorial limits of every species. 
The bats, being neither birds nor beasts, would not choose sides in the conflict. For this, a law 
was passed that forever condemned the bats to darkness. Yet one young bat, Shade Silverwing, dared to 
break the law.


RIP Notes
~~~~~~~~~
These rips were done with a high quality setting while attempting to keep the smallest size possible.

REBOOT.OP could have gone smaller, but he felt that 180MB an episode was good enough.

As with all of our releases, we suggest using VLC Media Player as it has the best possiblity
to work with our releases.

Please note that this release did not have any subtitles on the disks, so if you do want
subs, please find them or make them for us.
